Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.31,0:00:18.34,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I have a big gun, I took it from my Lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.55,0:00:21.79,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Sick with Justice, I just wanna feel you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.02,0:00:25.20,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'm your angel, only a ring away...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.32,0:00:28.55,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You make me violate you, no matter who you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.53,0:00:38.67,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}It's all up to you, no one lives forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.87,0:00:42.26,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Been burn in the hell, by all those pigs out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.34,0:00:45.53,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}It's always been hell, from when I was born...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.67,0:00:48.72,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}They make me violate them, no matter who they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.72,0:00:52.26,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs79}Get down on your knees! Get a good head on your shoulders!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.26,0:00:55.69,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}If it's for your guys, go to the end of the Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.69,0:00:59.00,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Do what you think, give it with dedication...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.00,0:01:02.27,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'll put out your misery!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.36,0:01:05.67,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You made a mess! For Christ sakes, this rotten world!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.67,0:01:09.10,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Shit out of luck! Go with my vision!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.10,0:01:12.54,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Light up the fire! Right on the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.54,0:01:15.90,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Weapon... I have it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.94,0:01:24.48,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Weapon... I have it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.09,0:01:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roanapur. In this city, gangs from\Naround the world fight for territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.76,0:01:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a strange balancing game.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.20,0:01:43.69,Top Secondary Dialog 1080P,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is a terrible tragedy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.77,0:01:46.74,Top Secondary Dialog 1080P,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The exterior of the building{\i0}\N{\i1}no longer has shape or form.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.81,0:01:48.57,Top Secondary Dialog 1080P,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What we know so far is that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.64,0:01:51.37,Top Secondary Dialog 1080P,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...37 embassy employees{\i0}\N{\i1}have been killed and 150 wounded.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.44,0:01:57.61,Top Secondary Dialog 1080P,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Zaire military is currently{\i0}\N{\i1}continuing with its rescue efforts.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.25,0:02:02.08,Top Secondary Dialog 1080P,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right after the bombing, a terrorist{\i0}\N{\i1}organization calling themselves...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.15,0:02:05.09,Top Secondary Dialog 1080P,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the Protectors of the Islamic Front...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.16,0:02:06.95,Top Secondary Dialog 1080P,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...claimed responsibility for the attack.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.15,0:02:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This sure is a dirty room.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.16,0:02:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy, are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.03,0:02:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a job.\NDutch says it's an emergency. Revy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.37,0:02:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you, Rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.77,0:02:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's a big,\Nlast minute request.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.84,0:02:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He told me to hurry and wake you up,\Nso I flew down here from the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.94,0:02:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.\NWho's this job for?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.05,0:02:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Chang.\NFrom the Triad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.76,0:02:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting\Nfor a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.23,0:02:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't this shop even offer a cup\Nof coffee? You call this service, Dutch?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.30,0:02:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I never knew\Nwe were running a café.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.50,0:02:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know why we have a torpedo boat,\Ndon't you, Mr. Chang?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.51,0:02:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such cold words, Dutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.08,0:03:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were burned out of our place\Nand came straight here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.18,0:03:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it common courtesy\Nto at least offer a cup of tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.85,0:03:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sure was a tragedy,\NMr. Chang.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.88,0:03:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I hear right, that half\Nof your office has collapsed?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.95,0:03:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we got hit hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.19,0:03:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it the Russians?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.82,0:03:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.16,0:03:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're always very friendly with\NMiss Balalaika. Hey, Two Hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.60,0:03:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I miss a lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.07,0:03:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we're just about to get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.37,0:03:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the cause of everything.\NBut it's certainly worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.44,0:03:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took this from a stupid Bulgarian...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.85,0:03:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...who tried to make a quick buck\Nin my territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't recall giving permission\Nto anyone to sell weapons...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.39,0:03:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...other than old Yolanda\Nfrom the Ripoff Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this guy clearly misunderstood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.66,0:03:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was casually selling guns on the\Nstreet as if he was selling hot shrimp.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.70,0:03:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To make matters worse, he mistook\Nmy warnings for some crazy joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.24,0:03:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He finally understood\Nand made a deal with us...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.27,0:04:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...when we were about to crush\Nhis balls like nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.38,0:04:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy was a real idiot, but it turns out\Nhe had an interesting job.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.55,0:04:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He worked for\NBulgarian Intelligence, Dutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.52,0:04:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This city is a comfortable place\Nfor folks like that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally a guy like that\Nis very useful, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.90,0:04:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time his playing\Nwith fire cost him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.67,0:04:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what he offered us\Nto save his balls, Dutch?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.10,0:04:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Documents.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.17,0:04:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.54,0:04:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hiking charts of a certain\Namusing little group.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.68,0:04:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The job they did just before us\Nhas been on TV all morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.48,0:04:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The U.S. Embassy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.02,0:04:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I smell danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The "ball boy's" real job\Nwas with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.13,0:04:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world's full of folks\Nwho want Uncle Sam to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.66,0:05:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told one of those groups\Nthat they dropped something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.00,0:05:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But as soon as I quoted the guys\Nwhat it would cost them...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.57,0:05:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...they told me to get the hell out of\Nthere before my ass becomes roast.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is how I answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.01,0:05:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"All right, then I'll go elsewhere."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.85,0:05:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to that, my office\Nhas been blasted all the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.12,0:05:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to somewhere around Jordan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.29,0:05:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and as they predicted, my ass\Nnearly became roast before I got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.23,0:05:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys are really not much fun.\NSo, Dutch. Here's the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.40,0:05:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to deliver this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.67,0:05:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five teams will leave Roanapur\Nat the same time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.41,0:05:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...each heading\Nto a different destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.98,0:05:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are five cases,\Nbut only one bingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.38,0:05:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- A feint.\N- As insurance, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your goal is the local base on Basilan\NIsland. The time limit is two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.32,0:06:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, my company\Nwill have left Basilan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.36,0:06:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chang, my man,\Ntwo days doesn't give us enough time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.00,0:06:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's always going to be too soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.60,0:06:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night's embassy bombing\Nwas the beginning of a chain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.74,0:06:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In two days the next schedule starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.37,0:06:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When they're done hiking\Nthere's gonna be a new president.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.31,0:06:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle Sam came to me\Nbecause their embassy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was launched into the air\Nlike the Apollo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll provide you\Nwith a getaway driver and guard...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.06,0:06:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...upon your arrival to the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.93,0:06:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, Dutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.86,0:06:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you bring our pay here with you?\NExpenses will be calculated separately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.13,0:06:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.37,0:06:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R! P! G!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well. They sure are quick.\NThey're already here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.28,0:06:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.52,0:07:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your information's leaked, Mr. Chang.\NThis job's canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.42,0:07:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna quit? If so, you're gonna\Nhave to pay the repair bills for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.32,0:07:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll at least escort you to your boat. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.83,0:07:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been in the field in a while.\NWhere's your emergency exit?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.23,0:07:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lead the way, Chang.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.03,0:07:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- A grenade?!\N- Don't panic, Two Hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.63,0:07:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.37,0:07:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if you hesitate, you lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.18,0:07:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chang's cleared the way.\NLet's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.81,0:08:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You're getting careless, boss.\N- Keep the bragging down, Two Hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have the skills, but you\Nstill fail to see the overall picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.47,0:08:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I admit I'm not at your level.\NI'll be wise and stick with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.51,0:08:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.24,0:08:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sending a car.\NGo to the harbor with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.18,0:08:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, boy. One of these days, I'd like to do\Na job that doesn't require risking my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop complaining, Dutch.\NWe're about to do the dirty work. Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.22,0:08:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave the rest to you,\NMr. Chang!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.12,0:08:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is such a pain in the ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.33,0:08:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you get there,\Ndon't forget the password.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.50,0:08:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The password is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.01,0:09:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.45,0:09:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our comrades have found the\Ndelivery boys on the main road.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.62,0:09:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can shed their blood\Nnear Ban Kantang.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.35,0:09:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.99,0:09:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This job should've been finished\Nafter the bombing of the Triad office.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.70,0:09:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in no mood to judge\Nthe failure of our comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.80,0:09:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mocked those guys\Nas simple gangsters...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.87,0:09:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but Chang turned out to be a much\Nsmarter gangster than you thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.57,0:09:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"See the enemy you should respect,\Nnot the enemy you despise."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.81,0:09:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words of Mao Tse-Tung.\NYou could learn from them, Ibraha.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.52,0:09:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moral discourse of a man who\Ndoesn't believe in God. It's worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.92,0:09:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's right.\NBesides, I don't believe in God either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.53,0:09:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're my comrade,\NTakenaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.80,0:10:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... More importantly, maybe we\Nshould speed up the plan in America.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.40,0:10:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous. The FBI\Nhas been keeping a close watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.71,0:10:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we move now before the feint,\Nthe plan will be ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.74,0:10:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To figure out which\Nof the five routes they've taken...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.11,0:10:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the first one to rule out is over land.\NAnd flying is too visible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.58,0:10:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That only leaves a sea route.\NDo you have proof?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's intuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.06,0:10:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will ask a comrade commander\Nin the Philippines for assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.73,0:10:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the sea route,\NI guess I'll have to take care of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.20,0:10:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the final step in\Nchanging the world, Takenaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.97,0:10:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.87,0:10:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The sea is so wide, and it is so big...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.31,0:10:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear the password?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.78,0:10:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Triad is super cool!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.98,0:10:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss Chang can handle himself\Nand has great style...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.62,0:10:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but when it comes to telling jokes,\Nhe couldn't be worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.32,0:10:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you're never gonna\Nfind someone perfect at everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.29,0:11:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You found it? A torpedo boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.30,0:11:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chang's got some interesting friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.70,0:11:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've determined their path, too?\NThat's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.74,0:11:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just as we predicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.81,0:11:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I don't have to trade in my ticket for\Nanother flight. I'm already in transit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.11,0:11:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just don't do anything\Nuntil I arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.52,0:11:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to confirm\Na few things. Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}E- Excuse me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.69,0:11:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please lend me your lighter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.30,0:11:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Are you from Japan, too?\N- Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.10,0:11:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.37,0:11:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.50,0:11:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- ...the way you held your hand.\N- I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, we're on a family trip\Nto Cebu Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.11,0:11:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I imagine any place\Noutside Manila would seem far...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.28,0:11:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- ...when traveling with a family.\N- Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.12,0:12:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Could we possibly\Nhave met before?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.29,0:12:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get this feeling\Nthis isn't the first time we've met.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.29,0:12:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.10,0:12:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're thinking of Mr. Ken.\NPeople always say I look like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.03,0:12:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, bye now. I'm awkward\Nwhen it comes to conversations.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.87,0:12:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.81,0:12:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are aloof.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.04,0:12:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you recognize\Nme from somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.44,0:12:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it would be\Nat the police station.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.65,0:12:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got them, Dutch.\NThe noisy little fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okay.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.76,0:12:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock, bring me the Remington.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.93,0:12:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- And the Hydra API for ammunition.\N- Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.94,0:13:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've taken out the enemy's eyes,\Nbut it may not be the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.55,0:13:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock. We'll be bait,\Nand charge past Basilan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you and Revy\Nto get off at Zamboanga...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and use the Zodiac\Nto get to Basilan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.55,0:13:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ibraha! I can't hear you!\NHurry and get down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Takenaka! Where are you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.80,0:13:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Basilan? Hey! That's where\Nour diversion team is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.23,0:13:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't panic!\NYeah, I'm at their camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.61,0:13:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lighthouse's base\Nis always the darkest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.67,0:13:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're waiting here\Nfor the first blow...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.14,0:13:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...among the local guerrillas...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.01,0:13:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but it's the same for them, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.92,0:13:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only place an American imperialist\Ncan come and go...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.75,0:13:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is the anti-guerrilla special\Noperations camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.16,0:13:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just further on from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.13,0:13:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can see Chang's next move.{\i0}\N{\i1}This is gonna be fun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.50,0:13:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a game, Takenaka! This is\Nan important precursor to the plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.10,0:13:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think of this as an exchange\Nof pawns, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.37,0:14:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, do you think there's anything\Nin this world that isn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.44,0:14:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the ones poised\Nto take the next piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.28,0:14:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sure is hard-headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.31,0:14:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What good is it if you can't have\Na little fun along the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.22,0:14:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, once we deliver the documents\Nwe'll meet you at the base.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.69,0:14:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'll come and get you\Nwhen I lose those guys clinging to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.19,0:14:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People who fight for a cause\Nare so damn persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.67,0:14:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. I have an additional message\Nfrom Mr. Chang.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.07,0:14:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Rock comes back\Nfrom the bathroom, tell him too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.27,0:14:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.78,0:14:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The target is moving further north\Nfrom the Zamboanga coast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.62,0:14:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So they passed Basilan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.72,0:14:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Basilan is already behind us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.72,0:14:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We believe they'll be heading\Ndue north from Negros.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- {\i1}We will continue our pursuit.{\i0}\N- Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:15:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not what it seems.\NThey're coming here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.60,0:15:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...right here to Basilan.\NThere's no mistaking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.94,0:15:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such an uninteresting, dull island.\NWhat time is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.18,0:15:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost six. That was more trouble\Nthan we expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.38,0:15:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...finding a place to come ashore.\NThe village should be right ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.02,0:15:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is quiet here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.86,0:15:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a ghost village with no people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's been martial law here\Nfor the last two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police and the guerrillas are\Nshooting lead...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.53,0:15:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...at each other day and night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.90,0:15:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people here must have run away\Nto more developed islands.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.26,0:16:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I keep you waiting?\NYou're from Lagoon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.66,0:16:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that there were four of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.67,0:16:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- And why should I answer that?\N- No reason you should.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just me, him and a briefcase.\NThat's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.97,0:16:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I don't see your partner.\NWhere's your guard?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.01,0:16:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's running around\Nlooking for a bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.12,0:16:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't know the difference\Nbetween beer and Volvic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.79,0:16:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, let's cut to the chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.39,0:16:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Triad is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, how did that one go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.49,0:16:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the time for jokes. If you don't\Nget to the point, I'll shoot you in the face.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.43,0:16:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey. Don't get so hot.\NIt was just a little joke to break the ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.17,0:16:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Triad is super cool. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.08,0:16:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must say, his sense of humor\Nis a little off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.85,0:16:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.28,0:17:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. But I didn't think it was\Nthat bad for Mr. Chang.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.59,0:17:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly, asshole.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.92,0:17:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a message\Nfrom the boss for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.93,0:17:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I am {\i1}tai san fu kwan."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.40,0:17:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what that means?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.53,0:17:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The god of death and punishment shall\Nhereby bring down judgment on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.34,0:17:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know where\Nyou got the password...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.11,0:17:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but Boss Chang isn't the pathetic\Nidiot or fool you assume him to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.18,0:17:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He prepared a new password\Nbecause of shit heads like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.58,0:17:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You hopped into this parade\Nwith your ass hanging out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.55,0:17:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Laugh, won't you? This is\Nthe part where you laugh. C'mon, laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.36,0:17:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, boy. I guess I got\Na little carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.20,0:17:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting handled like this by a little girl\Nlike you. How embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.84,0:17:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock! Get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.05,0:18:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Rock!\NYou screwed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.63,0:18:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The gunfire's started.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.03,0:18:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.53,0:18:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leigharch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.87,0:18:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's such a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.00,0:18:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to relax too much\Nbefore work. I made that clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.88,0:18:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna move\Nuntil the gunfire dies down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.11,0:18:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they die,\Nwe don't get paid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.82,0:18:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- I don't feel like it.\N- No, work's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.23,0:18:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! They keep coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.53,0:18:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That dumbass idiot Rock!\NDamn him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.43,0:18:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister! Lower your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.78,0:19:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Are you the getaway driver?!\N- Do I look like an attorney?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.45,0:19:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was rude, bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go after them! The military's\Nleft their camp! Retreat! Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.59,0:19:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard from Mr. Chang that\Nthere were four of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.63,0:19:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the other three?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.66,0:19:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plans changed and it became two of us.\NThen one messed up and was captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.27,0:19:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! That is pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.77,0:19:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going straight to the base.\NI wanna finish this job and go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.61,0:19:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's their hideout?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,North of the village. Six miles.\NIt's in the jungle. Yes it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.64,0:19:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not going to the military base.\NWe'll take care of those other guys first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.15,0:19:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wipe your own damn ass.\NOr tell that to the cavalry, Mary Read.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.46,0:19:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our job is to take you to the base.\NThat's all. And we get paid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.59,0:19:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not interested in\Ndoing anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:20:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My partner has the documents. Get it?\NUnderstand you yes? "Yes it is" lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.84,0:20:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stain the seats, Shen Hua.\NIf you're gonna do it, do it outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.87,0:20:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My English is not too good\Nbecause I'm pure Taiwanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.11,0:20:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it no big deal if your head gets\Nseparated from the rest of your body?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.05,0:20:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.08,0:20:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think the boss hired you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.89,0:20:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The documents.\NWithout the documents...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.22,0:20:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it'll be us three idiots\Nin this car who will...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.39,0:20:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...have to do the twist in front of the boss\Nwith dimwitted looks on our faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.77,0:20:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.71,0:20:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've formed an alliance.\NThis camp is now under our command.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.68,0:20:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's perfect. Now, welcome to\Nour demilitarized zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.62,0:20:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We saw what's inside\Nthe briefcase. It's empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.05,0:21:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know nothing about it. And even if I did,\NI couldn't answer. You know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.39,0:21:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An untwisted answer. At a time like this,\Nyou should at least crack a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.20,0:21:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we have time.\NWe can talk this through.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.40,0:21:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, shall we do this\Nin Japanese, young man?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.97,0:21:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're gonna get involved\Nin this kinda stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.18,0:21:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you really need to be\Na bit more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.91,0:21:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Japanese, aren't you? How long\Nhave you been doing this kinda work?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.09,0:21:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you're no fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.52,0:21:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna stay quiet?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.49,0:21:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't hurt\Nfor us fellow countrymen...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.59,0:21:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...be friendly to each other,\Nnow would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.87,0:21:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.52,0:23:18.52,Black Lagoon Next Episode,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10\pos(980,916)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.32,0:23:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has the launderer's delivery boy\Narrived yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.63,0:23:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late, Langley boys!
